ational_team\"}, {\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999966771611, \"rank\": 3.322790114024739e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she did so with a French-girl ensemble in an on-theme Dijon mustard-colored suit.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Portman was spotted in the star-studded stands at the Women's Gymnastics Team Final in a yellow suit set with a structured blazer and the tiniest matching miniskirt.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rob_Portman\", \"score\": 0.9985598436495668, \"rank\": 0.0014422148748781346, \"text\": \"Portman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rob_Portman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rob_Portman\"}, {\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9030433960932454, \"rank\": 0.10713118500891444, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She layered the jacket over a white ribbed tee and styled the preppy ensemble with unexpected shoe: a black-and-white platform sneaker.\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Portman kept the rest of her accessories simple and finished off the 'fit with tousled waves and a red manicure.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Getty Images  Getty Images  During the broadcast, Portman could be seen cheering on Team USA, which includes Jordan Chiles, Suni Lee, Jade Carey, Hezly Rivera, and the G.O.A.T.,Simone Biles.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbp